5:
So you're planning a vacation in the
Endless Blue?
9:
We're still discussing it, but... I
thought you'd be more into the idea.
12:
Did you forget I'm from there? I've
seen enough blue to last me a
lifetime.
13:
There are way better places to take
me for a trip.
17:
Well, we're only in the planning
stage—
20:
Guess you'll be holding down the
fort while we're gone. That's too bad.
25: I never said I WOULDN'T go—
30:
What was that place called again,
Alk? Paradise somethin' or other?
Like some fancy getaway for rich
folks.
35:
Yeah, Paradise Isle. It's a pretty
high-class resort they built on an
artificial island.
38:
Heard they've got fancy schmancy
night pools and other expensive
attractions.
41:
But I guess even a place like that
ain't nice enough for our lady's
tastes. What a shame!
51:
If you really want me to go so badly,
then I'll consider accompanying you!
54:
No need to force yourself for our
sakes, yeah? I'll keep everyone
company while you're gone.
57:
What? Just say you wanna go if you
wanna go.
71:
You poopie, smelly, buttface! No one
loves you, you furry menace!
77:
Think you went a little overboard on
the teasing, Nimbus...
85:
I want to go on vacation with you.
Do you not feel the same?
92:
B-but only because I know how sad
you'll be without me! It's also
extremely rude not to accept an
invitation from a friend!
96:
Those are the only reasons why I'm
agreeing to this!
102:
Ahahaha! Come on, Stella! Get over
here already!
106:
What are the rest of you standing
around for? Hurry up before we
leave you behind!
110:
This is going exactly like we thought
it would, huh.
115: Ugh... She's such a pain in the ass.
119: Pot calling the kettle black here.
129:
Get a move on, slowpokes!
Oooh, what's that? It's so slimy!
134:
Well, at least someone's having the
time of her life.
160:
Really? Is that all you old farts got in
you? I expected better!
163:
Old? Really? Don't lump me in with
Light over there.
165:
I just know how to have fun like an
adult. Now run along and go splash
in the water or whatever.
168:
You're talking big for someone who
was super excited to go earlier.
171:
You really took that performance at
face value, huh?
175:
I'll have you know... I love a good
performance.
187:
Ooooh, so scawwey! What a big,
bad kitty cat!
200:
You know, Nimbus really does
become more child-like whenever
he's around Alice.
204: It's nice that he's made a friend.
209: I want to be friends too.
214:
Ahahaha! You sure you're not half
turtle? Try to keep up!
